1. *Predivna* je ova planina! (This mountain is *beautiful*!)
2. Ovde ima mnogo *predivnih* mesta za posetiti. (There are many *beautiful* places to visit here.)
3. Ona peva *predivno*. (She sings *beautifully*.)
4. Oni su bili *predivni* prema meni. (They were *wonderful* to me.)
5. *Predivno* je videti te opet. (It's *lovely* to see you again.)
6. Ona je *predivno* odevena. (She is *beautifully* dressed.)
7. *Predivan* pogled! (What a *gorgeous* view!)
8. Njihova veza je bila *predivna*. (Their relationship was *wonderful*.)
9. Ona ima *predivan* glas. (She has a *beautiful* voice.)
10. To je bilo *predivno* iskustvo. (It was a *wonderful* experience.)

Note: The word "predivan" can be translated to English as "beautiful," "lovely," "gorgeous," or "wonderful," depending on the context.